01:07:35.780 --> 01:07:38.300 line:84%
sort of, what your
take on that is?

01:07:38.300 --> 01:07:39.680 line:90%
The historian's question?

01:07:39.680 --> 01:07:40.400 line:90%
Yeah.

01:07:40.400 --> 01:07:44.240 line:84%
Well, so much of '70s
