01:08:27.500 --> 01:08:33.500 line:84%
as we can see feminist themed
cultural products everywhere

01:08:33.500 --> 01:08:34.109 line:90%
we go.

01:08:34.109 --> 01:08:37.880 line:84%
And I chalk that
up as a positive.

01:08:37.880 --> 01:08:41.149 line:84%
It might not be the feminism
you particularly want to see,

01:08:41.149 --> 01:08:44.569 line:84%
you might be able to list
